snippet.title: DEVIL DEVOUR ALIVE DX - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Devil Devour Alive DX is a pick-up-and-play occult themed arcade game with an over the top 90s style. It supports vertical screen orientation (TATE MODE!!!!), online leaderboards, and unlockables. It also features retro 32-bit era style graphics, CRT shader, and spooky synthwave music.

DEVIL DEVOUR ALIVE DX (C) VIRTUA WORLDS, LLC
